<div class="story"><p>Kitty Hawk Woods is a subdivision spread out through the N.C. Coastal Reserve and National Estuarine Research <a href="http://www.nccoastalreserve.net/web/crp/kitty-hawk-woods" title="Reserve">Reserve</a> located in Kitty Hawk. The community of Kitty Hawk Woods enjoys the maritime forest environment provided by the preserve with hiking and kayaking nearby. You will find Kitty Hawk Woods behind the community of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/seascape.asp" title="Sea Scape">Sea Scape</a>. </p><p><a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/kittty-hawk-woods-covenants.pdf" title="Kitty Hawk Woods Covenants" target="_blank">Kitty Hawk Woods Covenants </a>These documents may not be the most up to date so, before you use this information to make a decision, you need to verify that these documents have not changed. This should help you get a feel for the character of the neighborhood. With most of our owners living out of state there are a number of developments that do not have an active Home Owners Association and in some instances the restrictive covenants and bylaws are no longer applicable.</p>
  </div>